Hng Dn S Dng
1. Giao din u tin khi ngi qun l m chng trnh. Form c thit k vi
hnh nn c trng cho cng vic qun l khch sn. Cc Button c minh ha
bng hnh nh d hiu, c trng cho tng chc nng.
Hnh nh giao din form chnh
T giao din ta c th thy chc nng qun l cc thng tin c bn lin quan n
n mt Khch sn.
2. Thao tc u tin khi ngi qun l s dng l vic ng nhp vo h thng
thng qua ti khon.
Hnh nh Giao din ng Nhp
ng nhp thnh cng form qun l chnh s hin ra nh trong hnh 1.
Hnh 1
Cc button :
- Button Khch Hng
Hnh nh button:
Khi Khch Hng c m ra. Ngi qun l s thao tc trn form Khch Hng
Giao din Form Khch hng
- Button Phng
Hnh nh button:
Khi Qun L Phng c m ra, ngi qun l s thao tc trn form Qun l
phng nh Thm, Sa, Xa thng tin phng.
Giao din Form Phng
- Button Trang Thit b
Hnh nh button
Khi Trang thit b c m ra, ngi qun l s thao tc trn form nh Thm,
Sa, Xa thng tin cc trang thit b c trong phng hoc ca khch sn.
Hnh nh giao din Trang thit b
- Button Dch v
Hnh nh button
Khi Dch v c m ra. Ngi qun l s thao tc trn form Dch v nh
Thm, Sa, Xa mt s dch v.
Hnh nh giao din Dch v
- Button Qun l Dch v
Hnh nh button
Khi Qun L Dch V c m ra. Ngi qun l s thao tc trn form Qun
L Dch V nh thm, sa, xa dch v cho tng phng.
Hnh nh giao din Qun l dch v
- Button Qun L Phng
Hnh nh button
Khi Qun L Phng c m ra. Ngi qun l s thao tc trn form Qun
L Phng nh sp xp vic ng k phng ca khch hng.
Hnh nh giao din Qun l Phng
- Button Qun L Trang Thit B
Hnh nh button
Khi Qun L Trang Thit B c m ra. Ngi qun l s thao tc trn form
Qun L Trang Thit B nh qun l cc trang thit b c trong tng phng.
Hnh nh giao din Qun l trang thit b
- Button Hng Dn
Hnh nh button
Khi form Hng Dn s c m ra. Form c tc dng gii thiu sn phm
v hng dn s dng phn mm.
Hnh nh giao din hng dn
- Button Log Out
Ngi qun l s tr li giao din ng nhp.
